{"type": "article", "id": 30605, "title": "极简腕表", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-04T22:58:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/201608042130504xAaC1IuZBJywMQD.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>苏格兰腕表品牌 <a href=\"https://nomadwatches.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nomad</a> 联手工业设计师 <a href=\"http://samuelwilkinson.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Samuel Wilkinson</a> 花费两年时间打造了这个名为 Line 的极简风格腕表，其中包括 Inline 和 Outline 两种款式。相比 Outline 看上去颇为密集的表盘设计，Inline 在外圈做了留白处理并且只标注了四个刻度。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/nomadwatches/the-line-collection-uncompromising-everyday-watche\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 95 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804215413lx45tLGJ1p8NhzAg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804215413R4o73Ny62BLviDhl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804215413KoutNLxTDzcapn0O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.606667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804215413BgKdTmrR8DwpCkAf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}